Just sent the following updated proposal to Casey and Sean -- Casey,
Hereâ€™s the revised pricing proposal for your four pharmacy locations. A few points of note:
Each site now includes a PoE switch.
For the McCoy Tygart location, I originally quoted an MX67 instead of the correct MX67Wâ€”the version with built-in Wi-Fi. I apologize for the oversight and have corrected it in this proposal.
â€‹eâ€™ll provide secure VPN connectivity between locations, VPN client access for up to 10 users, and remote setup support with someone from your team (Sean Brasseal) assisting onsite during each turn-up.
Each managed location includes full management and monitoring of the firewall, Wi-Fi, and switch, along with ongoing licensing for those devices.
Regarding Woodlands (the Ubiquiti location): while this site wonâ€™t support Ciscoâ€™s Auto VPN process and its associated enhancements, a standard site-to-site VPN is still achievable. Iâ€™ve noted a few key points below, and Iâ€™m happy to walk through the technical details if youâ€™d like to explore further.

McCoy Tygart Drug â€“ 821 N Rock St, Sheridan, AR
Upfront Cost:
â€“ Cisco Meraki MX67W firewall with integrated Wi-Fi: $1100
â€“ Cisco Meraki MR28 access point for extended Wi-Fi coverage: $450
â€“ Cisco Meraki MS130-48P switch: $2,900
Total Upfront: $4,450
Monthly Service: $275/month

Sheridan Family Pharmacy â€“ 677 Heritage Dr, Sheridan, AR
Upfront Cost:
â€“ Cisco Meraki Z4 firewall with integrated Wi-Fi: $500
â€“ Cisco Meraki MS130-24P switch: $1,650
Total Upfront: $2,150

Redfield Pharmacy â€“ 1011 Sheridan Rd, Redfield, AR
Upfront Cost:
â€“ Cisco Meraki Z4 firewall with integrated Wi-Fi: $500
â€“ Cisco Meraki MS130-24P switch: $1,650
Total Upfront: $2,150
Monthly Service: $165/month

Woodlands Pharmacy â€“ 7197 Sheridan Rd #109, White Hall, AR
Currently, equipment and management for this location have been arranged through one of your partners. While this site does not support Ciscoâ€™s Auto VPN process and its associated enhancements, a standard site-to-site VPN is still achievableâ€”though it may be slightly more complex to configure and maintain over time. We will assist with setting up the VPN connection from this site to the main McCoy Tygart location, with the understanding that your other partner will be responsible for completing the configuration on their end and supporting any technical issues that may arise with their equipment in the future. No monthly fee will apply to this site unless we are asked to manage it as well. Please note that remote access to this locationâ€”from Sheridan, Redfield, or external usersâ€”may require additional setup and could incur separate charges from either Vantix or your Ubiquiti partner.

Summary:
Total Upfront (all sites): $8,750
Total Monthly Recurring: $605/month

Let me know if you have any questions or are ready for me to send a service agreement.

Thanks again,
Stan
